snippet.title: Megaquarium: Architect's Collection (Trailer)
snippet.description:
The Architect's Collection adds brand new structural elements such as bridges and tunnels, 15 iconic animals and a plethora of new tools to design and decorate your aquarium with. This ambitious expansion will take your aquarium design skills to new heights!

For more information check out: https://www.twicecircled.com/megaquarium/

Sign up to the dev newsletter here:
https://www.twicecircled.com/

http://www.twitter.com/twicecircled
